title: Living The Abundant Life | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Living The Abundant Life | Joel Osteen
description:
God wants you to live an abundant life. Enlarge your vision and watch Him take you to new levels of joy, victory and favor. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
